---

<section class="how">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="eyebrow">03 &mdash; How it works</div>
      <h2>Three steps. Then it just works.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-label">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <h3>Install</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Run one command in Claude Code. The skill installs the script, sets up your config directory, and kicks off an AI-assisted session to build your guide from existing dotfiles.</p>
        <div class="term">
          <div class="term-bar">
            <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="term-body">
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-prompt">$</span> npx skills add halpme-sh/halpme
            </div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">Installing halpme skill...</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">Setting up ~/.config/halpme...</div>
            <div class="term-line term-success">&#10003; halpme ready</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-label">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <h3>Add your notes</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Drop a Markdown file in <code>~/.config/halpme/</code>. Each file is a topic. Use the annotation convention to set the keyword and description that appear in your guide.</p>
        <div class="term">
          <div class="term-bar">
            <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
            <span class="term-path">~/.config/halpme/git.md</span>
          </div>
          <div class="term-body">
            <div class="term-line term-comment">### Git Workflow</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">&lt;!-- halpme: git | Daily aliases --&gt;</div>
            <div class="term-spacer"></div>
            <div class="term-line term-comment">### Undo a commit</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">&lt;!-- halpme: git | Undo without losing work --&gt;</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">&#96;git reset --soft HEAD~1&#96;</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-label">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <h3>Find anything</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Type <code>halpme</code> to browse your full guide, or <code>halpme &lt;topic&gt;</code> to jump straight to a section. Rendered by glow, right in your terminal.</p>
        <div class="term">
          <div class="term-bar">
            <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="term-body">
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-prompt">$</span> halpme git
            </div>
            <div class="term-spacer"></div>
            <div class="term-line term-heading">git &middot; Daily aliases &amp; undo commands</div>
            <div class="term-rule">&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">Git Workflow</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">Undo a commit</div>
            <div class="term-line term-dim">Stashing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how {
    padding: var(--section-pad-y) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .step-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-label);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--n-100);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* terminal windows */
  .term {
    background: var(--term-bg);
    border-radius: var(--r-term);
    border: 1px solid var(--term-border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-term);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .term-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--term-titlebar);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--term-border);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .dot-red    { background: var(--dot-red); }
  .dot-yellow { background: var(--dot-yellow); }
  .dot-green  { background: var(--dot-green); }

  .term-path {
    margin-left: 8px;
    color: var(--term-dim);
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .term-body {
    padding: 14px 16px 18px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--term-text);
  }

  .term-line { display: block; }

  .term-prompt { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8px; }
  .term-dim    { color: var(--term-dim); }
  .term-success { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .term-comment { color: var(--accent); }
  .term-heading { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .term-spacer  { height: 10px; }

  .term-rule {
    color: #3A352F;
    margin: 3px 0 6px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
